        "id": 8341
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-02-11T22:55:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Would be nice to abstract this integration, since the velocity update rule is largely shared by the difference force affectors. It doesn\u0027t need to go so far as having an interface that lets integrators get swapped around, but something UpdateVelocity(force, dt, \u0026linearVel) or linearVel +\u003d IntegrateForce(force, dt)?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 20,
        "startChar": 32,
        "endLine": 20,
        "endChar": 59
      },
      "revId": "ddabbf359803776758bc5299eb098cc5fd73ceee",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
