      },
      "lineNbr": 20,
      "author": {
        "id": 5631
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-02-12T18:29:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, that would be nice. As I mentioned elsewhere, I think that three of these are going to collapse into one that just uses SkCurve, which is sufficient to describe all of the different force behaviors (except for point-force). I\u0027ll definitely extract that logic when I do that refactor.",
      "parentUuid": "37db6fc3_487d4a94",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 20,
        "startChar": 32,
        "endLine": 20,
        "endChar": 59
      },
      "revId": "ddabbf359803776758bc5299eb098cc5fd73ceee",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
